properties.headline: Winter Storm Warning issued January 28 at 9:03PM AKST until January 29 at 9:00AM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Accumulations of around 6 inches expected

* WHERE...Yakutat area.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM AKST Wednesday. Some mixing with rain is
possible.

* IMPACTS...The hazardous conditions could impact the morning
commute. Snow will be heavy and wet.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Expect a change to all rain as winds shift
south Wednesday morning.
properties.instruction:
If you must travel, keep an extra flashlight, food, and water in
your vehicle in case of an emergency. Prepare for possible power
outages.

NWSheadline: WINTER STORM WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM AKST WEDNESDAY... ...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY WILL EXPIRE AT 9 PM AKST THIS EVENING
